headline: Rokid Sets Stage for AI Glasses Launch in New York
summary: Rokid, a pioneer in human-computer interaction and AR innovation, announced the upcoming launch event for the Rokid Glasses, the world's lightest full-function AI & AR smart glasses. The event, titled "Future in Sight," will take place on August 26, 2025, in New York City. The event will bring together media, industry experts, and partners for an immersive experience that showcases how Rokid is shaping the next era of wearable computing.
